member.name: T:Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Infrastructure.ILazyLoader

summary.para: A service that can be injected into entities to give them the capability of loading navigation properties automatically the first time they are accessed.

The service lifetime is 'ServiceLifetime.Transient'. This means that each entity instance will use its own instance of this service. The implementation may depend on other services registered with any lifetime. The implementation does not need to be thread-safe.

member.remarks: See Lazy loading for more information.
